thread.title: Matthew Mella
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Matthew Mella

author: Matthew Mella
title: Matthew Mella
text:
Always a positive experience at StoreDJ. Friendly but not pushy staff, who have up to date knowledge, or can get it quickly.
Also I get a genuine feel that the staff are trying to help customers get the right gear for them, as opposed to best mark up for the sales assistant like some other places I've been in the past. Easy of course when your prices are the best in town.
